room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: I had a great time! My job sent the production team and front office team on a company outing. I was in the Cabin Fever room, and our operator Melissa was great. We did good!

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: Very fun! Great employees, like Kyler making the experience awesome. Have tried other escape room experiences and this place is my favorite so far. I have completed Cabin Fever and Abandoned School.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: Went there for my son's 12th bday. We did the Cabin Fever room and it was great! I highly recommend it for good family fun. Meghna was our host and she was terrific.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Austin Panic Room in Austin
review: We had a blast in the Cabin Fever room! It was a great place and it held our group of 10 without any problems! Great way to celebrate my 21 year olds birthday!
